metadata.title: FindingKing Leather Cord Necklaces Light Blue 18" 3Pcs
features: This is a beautiful new set of 3 light blue colored genuine leather necklaces
Each is finished with a sterling silver lobster claw clasp and sterling silver ends
Whether you wear these modern necklaces alone or with a pendant on them you will be adding a touch of beauty to any outfit
